This is a dataset hosted by the City of New York. 
The city has an open data platform and they update their information according to the amount of data that is brought in.
Below is the link to the dataset.

https://data.cityofnewyork.us/Public-Safety/Motor-Vehicle-Collisions-Crashes/h9gi-nx95/about_data

Anyone can easily export the dataset to the required data format from here.
